## Customization

### Adding More Agents

Copy additional agent files from the source repository to `.claude/agents/`:
- `planner.md` - Structured planning
- `architect.md` - Architecture decisions
- `tdd-guide.md` - Test-driven development
- `code-reviewer.md` - Code review assistance
- `security-reviewer.md` - Security audits
- `build-error-resolver.md` - Build issue resolution
- `e2e-runner.md` - End-to-end testing
- `doc-updater.md` - Documentation maintenance
- `refactor-cleaner.md` - Code cleanup

### Adding More MCP Servers

Edit `.claude.json` to add additional MCP servers. Available options:
- `github` - GitHub operations
- `supabase` - Supabase database
- `vercel` - Vercel deployments
- `railway` - Railway deployments
- `cloudflare-*` - Cloudflare services
- `context7` - Live documentation
- `memory` - Persistent memory
- `sequential-thinking` - Enhanced reasoning

### Modifying Hooks

Edit `.claude/settings.local.json` to customize hooks:
- `PreToolUse` - Runs before tool execution
- `PostToolUse` - Runs after tool execution
- `Stop` - Runs when session ends

### Disabling Components

- Remove files from `.claude/` directories
- Remove MCP servers from `.claude.json`
- Set `"hooks": {}` in settings.local.json to disable hooks

